 2 See for example Aljazeera&#8217;s <i>Code of Ethics 
</i></p>
<p>(http://english.aljazeera.net/aboutus/2006/11/2008525185733692771.html); the British Broadcasting 
Corporation&#8217;s <i>Editorial Guidelines </i>(www.bbc.co.uk/guidelines/editorialguidelines); Article 19&#8217;s 
<i>Camden Principles on freedom of expression and equality 
</i>(www.article19.org/advocacy/campaigns/camden-principles); and the International Federation of 
Journalist&#8217;s <i>The Ethical Journalism Initiative </i>(http://ethicaljournalisminitiative.org). </p>

